name: "Bite It You Scum"
description: seeing a lot of hatred for the community lately so I decided to take their hate and mint it to further piss them off even more. I'm all about post-ironic humor and I think sometimes it gets mistaken for me being a certain way when I'm actually making fun of whatever I am posing to be into at the time. I love cryptoart and the NFT community you all broke a spell of me not making anything for a really long time and I appreciate H=N to fullest
